{"tid":388645,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【學生自治不容干預　誓死捍衛言論自由——支援中大學生會】","createTime":"2017-09-05T15:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T23:57:42.000Z","uid":28366,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2807ca0e029773438a6a51719f988c69e0cc9c2","tid":388645,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"【學生自治不容干預　誓死捍衛言論自由&mdash;&mdash;支援中大學生會】<br />\n<br />\n中大學生會於今天在民主牆及學生會管轄用地內掛上「香港獨立」之橫額及海報，而中大學生事務處處長梁汝照表示「港獨」違反法例、不符合中大立場，派遣保安越權強行拆除掛於中大學生會轄下文化廣場之「香港獨立」橫額。<br />\n<br />\n大學本來就與社會息息相關，大學生作為知識份子，關心社會乃應作之事。而言論自由乃與生俱來的基本人權，試問中大學生會何罪之有，如何違反法例？大學乃創造知識之地，保障校園開放的風氣供莘莘學子討論反思，是教育之基本條件。更甚者，中大文化廣場乃中大學生會管轄用地，學生組織由學生自治，其獨立性及不容外力干預的特質乃學生會重要的意義。本會在此強烈讉責中大校方干預中大學生會自治，破壞香港言論自由。無論支持與否，學校亦應保障同學表達意見之權利。<br />\n<br />\n後記：教大學生會於中央廣場掛上「香港獨立」之橫額不足半小時，發現有操普通話之女學生偷偷毀壞學生會之橫額，強行扯爛橫額之繩索及黑布，學生會成員立即上前阻止，而該名女同學不作回應立即離去。<br />\n<br />\n本會在此讉責該名女同學之行為，同學有權表達個人意見，但即使不認同亦需尊重他人意見，因立場有異而破壞他人物品乃蠻夷之為，在此呼籲各位同學共同捍衛我們所有的權利與自由。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21232047_1603230916409619_7157162555777595601_n.jpg?oh=705aacd062038b67a8c6c91dacaed4d4&amp;oe=5A5102C8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21232047_1603230916409619_7157162555777595601_n.jpg%3Foh%3D705aacd062038b67a8c6c91dacaed4d4%26oe%3D5A5102C8&h=0663056c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21317549_1603230943076283_1575102587704006688_n.jpg?oh=b83e868450fa72d00ace2d4319e5b57f&amp;oe=5A170643\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21317549_1603230943076283_1575102587704006688_n.jpg%3Foh%3Db83e868450fa72d00ace2d4319e5b57f%26oe%3D5A170643&h=b21a0f33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EdUHKSUEC/photos/pcb.1603231866409524/1603230916409619/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEdUHKSUEC%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.1603231866409524%2F1603230916409619%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=6qqAiN5u0PIbtmxPefdDLePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=685046b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EdUHKSUEC/photos/pcb.1603231866409524/1603230916409619/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"4e5da788f39e4e536710c32c5b1d46b752d748e3","tid":388645,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e65ca714cf42e8273f57c84a27fd121e87191f","tid":388645,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:10:58.000Z","msg":"鬼鬼鼠鼠偷banner<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b07b60d8e231daadf395126d2ae85b901f8c9e","tid":388645,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:11:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼鬼鼠鼠偷banner<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570f3ba68c93b74db65e0370ba652a489ec3a93f","tid":388645,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417316e61e07e7aadd28bb85d729706259a927fa","tid":388645,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:20:08.000Z","msg":"班中國人做乜事capture the flag"},{"pid":"29436b351d57c71879ab569355327a84fd908ec5","tid":388645,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T15:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72038a5b9114b4af1451be07af4e6f9c9fa1a934","tid":388645,"uid